### Today Checklist
GET http://localhost:3000/api/today
Authorization: Bearer {{USER_ID}}

### Toggle Habit Completion
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/today
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{USER_ID}}

{
  "habitName": "Meditate",
  "completed": true,
  "notes": "Quick morning sit"
}

### Goals Overview
GET http://localhost:3000/api/goals?days=14
Authorization: Bearer {{USER_ID}}

### Weekly Plan Input
GET http://localhost:3000/api/week?hoursPerDay=3&historyDays=10
Authorization: Bearer {{USER_ID}}

### Weekly Review
GET http://localhost:3000/api/week/review?weekStart=2025-01-06
Authorization: Bearer {{USER_ID}}

### Sign In (placeholder)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/signin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "you@example.com"
}
